  "description": "This intracranial electroencephalography (iEEG) dataset comprises stereoelectroencephalography (SEEG) electrode recordings from pediatric patients with prior craniotomy undergoing epilepsy surgery evaluation. The dataset includes electrode coordinates localized in individual native post-operative CT imaging space, providing clinical neurophysiological data for assessing the safety and accuracy of SEEG implantation procedures in this patient population.",
